WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  Do you like to play with peg games, but always wanted to create
game boards of your own? If the answer is yes, then `Create_a_Q'
is for you!!

  You can create any type of game board you want, except an empty
board, in an area of 11x11 spaces, and of course play with it.

  When you run Create_a_Q, the game starts with a predefined game
board you can play with, and as with all my other 'Q' games you
can play it in two ways:

  -The 'Normal' game, you must jump over a peg and that peg will
   be removed.

  -The 'Inverted' game, you have to jump over an empty space and
   a peg will appear there.

  The 'Q Editor' option lets you change or create your own 'Q'
games, as well as loading or saving them on disk. The editor lets
you select the 'allowed' moves, if you want to permit the
vertical, horizontal and the diagonal moves.

  Have fun!

FEATURES
--------

-Simple installation: just run the game and play!

-A handy game board editor that lets you play, as well as load and
 save your own 'Q' boards.

-Small package, the Lha archive is smaller than 50K, so it doesn't
 take ages to download :)

-The game plays on the Workbench screen and its window is
 resizeable.

